Задача 1 - Обхождане на списък.

while_traverse.py

books = ["Learn You a Haskell", "The Healthy Programmer","Code Complete","The Pragmatic Programmer","Pro Git","Introduction to Algorithms","Concrete Mathematics"]
a = 0

while a < len(books) :
     print(books[a])
     a = 1 + a 

for_traverse.py

books = ["Learn You a Haskell", "The Healthy Programmer","Code Complete","The Pragmatic Programmer","Pro Git","Introduction to Algorithms","Concrete Mathematics"]

for book in books:
     print(book)


Задача 2 - Четене на променлив брой вход от потребителя.
read_n_numbers.py

n = input("Enter count of numbers: ")
n = int(n)

count = 1
numbers = []

while count <= n:
    number = input("Enter number: ")
    number = int(number)

    numbers = numbers + [number]

    count += 1

print(numbers)

